text.tspan: We just don’t know it at the time.
A healthy body and mind can be found in fresh air.
A golden opportunity will arrive in an unexpected way.
Everything will unravel under the moonlight.
The tides of change is the only thing that does not.
Your body will not fail you in the moment of truth.
Your finances will go through a period of considerable expansion,
The warmth of love will melt your worries away.
Successful ambitions require hard work but the rewards are even greater.
A good luck spell is cast upon you.
Bad luck will pass through you like it never existed.
You will experience a surge of energy and vitality.
Be assertive, your business choices will succeed.
Fire of passion burns like a giant bonfire.
If you set your mind to it you can do anything.
Winds of fortune bless only a few people every year.
Health is a gift, cherish it and it will last for a very long time.
Stay focused, keep your goals in mind and you will get financial success in the long run.
Stay sincere and things will go the way you want.
Unexpected epiphany will lead to advancements.
